5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

port

Generic function

Summary

Returns the port for the specified object.

Signature

port object => value

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

value
An instance of type false-or(<port>).

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the port used to display object.
